Cab aggregator Ola has launched its ride­sharing services Ola Share here in the city. Ola Share 
will allow users who travel on the same routes to share their cab rides with users from social 
groups they are part of, the company said in a statement.Cab aggregator Ola has launched its ride­sharing services Ola Share here in the city. Ola Share 
